How to make run
===============
NOTE:
For the first time, do all the following steps.
Afterwards, only the last three steps are needed.


sudo apt-get install vsftpd

sudo service vsftpd stop

edit /etc/vsftpd.conf by uncommenting the fowllowing lines
local_enable=YES
write_enable=YES
local_umask=022

sudo ./vsftpd

open another console:
make run

back to the first console:
CTRL^C
